"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-team-usa-track-and-field-roster-2024-olympics-sha-carri-richardson-arrives\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"USAtrack and fieldOlympic trials concluded on June 30 at the Hayward Field Stadium.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 83, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For almost a week, the world saw American athletes go neck-to-neck in competition to book their place in theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 84, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_football\", \"score\": 0.9966643649325005, \"rank\": 0.0033259986878116706, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition also saw several records being reset including the women's 400m hurdles world record.\\u00c2  The records keep getting broken and set, but very few rise back from setbacks likeSha'Carri Richardsondoes.\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The world champion was all set to battle Jamaicans for 100m Olympic gold at the Tokyo Olympics before she was suspended for marijuana usage, which she later claimed she took to cope with the death of her biological mother.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.465404079823002e-30, \"text\": \"Jamaicans\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A year later, she failed to qualify for the World Championships.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it has been a dream run for Richardson since the start of 2023.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.5488992875086414e-12, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From winning her maiden international title at the Doha Diamond League to becoming the world champion, the 24-year-old proved her doubters wrong.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson stormed to a world-leading 10.71s at the U.S. Olympic Trials, and now, she is an overwhelming favorite to end a long drought of 100m Olympic gold for the USA in Paris.\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.5488992875086414e-12, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794956577, \"rank\": 0.038961038961052005, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}, {\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999846932043, \"rank\": 1.069711936218974e-08, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9